#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.take.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.take"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:1 of
msgid "Return the elements in the given *positional* indices along an axis."
msgstr "返回沿轴的给定*位置*索引处的元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:3 of
msgid ""
"This means that we are not indexing according to actual values in the "
"index attribute of the object. We are indexing according to the actual "
"position of the element in the object."
msgstr ""
"这意味着我们不是根据对象索引属性中的实际值进行索引，而是根据元素在对象中"
"的实际位置进行索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:7 of
msgid "An array of ints indicating which positions to take."
msgstr "一个整数数组，指示要获取哪些位置的元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:9 of
msgid ""
"The axis on which to select elements. ``0`` means that we are selecting "
"rows, ``1`` means that we are selecting columns. For `Series` this "
"parameter is unused and defaults to 0."
msgstr ""
"选择元素的轴。``0`` 表示选择行，``1`` 表示选择列。对于 `Series`，此参数未"
"使用，默认为 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:13 of
msgid "For compatibility with :meth:`numpy.take`. Has no effect on the output."
msgstr "为了与 :meth:`numpy.take` 兼容。对输出没有影响。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:16 of
msgid "An array-like containing the elements taken from the object."
msgstr "一个类似数组的对象，包含从原对象中获取的元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:22 of
msgid "Select a subset of a DataFrame by labels."
msgstr "通过标签选择 DataFrame 的子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.iloc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:25 of
msgid "Select a subset of a DataFrame by positions."
msgstr "通过位置选择 DataFrame 的子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.take`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:28 of
msgid "Take elements from an array along an axis."
msgstr "沿轴从数组中获取元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:31 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:47 of
msgid "Take elements at positions 0 and 3 along the axis 0 (default)."
msgstr "沿轴 0（默认）获取位置 0 和 3 处的元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:49 of
msgid ""
"Note how the actual indices selected (0 and 1) do not correspond to our "
"selected indices 0 and 3. That's because we are selecting the 0th and 3rd"
" rows, not rows whose indices equal 0 and 3."
msgstr ""
"注意所选的实际索引（0 和 1）与我们选择的索引 0 和 3 不对应。这是因为我们"
"选择的是第 0 行和第 3 行，而不是索引等于 0 和 3 的行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:58 of
msgid "Take elements at indices 1 and 2 along the axis 1 (column selection)."
msgstr "沿轴 1（列选择）获取索引 1 和 2 处的元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.take.take:67 of
msgid ""
"We may take elements using negative integers for positive indices, "
"starting from the end of the object, just like with Python lists."
msgstr ""
"我们可以使用负整数作为正索引，从对象末尾开始获取元素，就像 Python 列表"
"一样。"

